NameofManga: Abandoned Wife Has A New Husband
Author: HanHa-Yeon,Lobster,
Description: “It's a wife sale.” Chloe is eventually abandoned by her coercive and violent husband. It is also a disgraceful 'selling wife'. When Chloe is in danger of being sold for three hundred yuan in front of a shabby, cramped bar and men who are no less than a bar. A mysterious man named Ash Brinicle appears.
